{"root":{"data":{"id":"djmsnbljwao0","created":1782864298058,"text":"SOP相关"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djmue5d33yg0","created":1782869221428,"text":"备注","layout_mind_offset":{"x":-52.99999842047674,"y":159.99999523162865}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djmuh4q0s5s0","created":1782869455125,"text":"lk抬头里面的","expandState":"expand"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djmufgl0h7c0","created":1782869324216,"text":"确保部件开料平整，没有粗糙。否则，油第⼀次粘合剂或底油前需要打磨或打砂，以使部件表⾯平整光滑。","layout_right_offset":{"x":5.750011395662511,"y":-34.24999940767901}},"children":[]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"djmufnkb4co0","created":1782869339411,"text":"油边","layout_mind_offset":{"x":369.999988973141,"y":-95.99999713897711}},"children":[]}]},"template":"default","theme":"fresh-blue","version":"1.4.43"}